cdata.name: Legolas Exchange
cdata.desc: The Legolas Exchange is an exchange that runs onan hybridmodel, incorporatinga decentralized ledger within its proprietary centralized platform in a bid to provideunalterability, temporality, and transparency of the order book.The exchange system is fueled by the LGO token, an ERC-20 token based on ethereum used to pay for Order fees and other paid services provided by Legolas.
